node.text: Dressed to impress! The @snapple story is a New York story, built from humble beginnings in the city’s corner stores. Snapple and A$AP Ferg are raising funds to help corner stores that were impacted by the Covid-19 pandemic. 100% of sales from the limited-time only Snapple merch collection will go to The Bodega and Small Business Group. Click the link in my bio to support the cause! #ASnappleCornerStory #ad #SnapplePartner
